snippet.title: QP Shooting - Dangerous!! Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay preview footage for QP Shooting - Dangerous!!, coming soon on Steam!

QP Shooting - Dangerous!! is a bullet hell type shoot'em'up developed by Orange_Juice and localized by Fruitbat Factory.
